THIS HOME IS EQUIPPED WITH ACCORDION-STYLE HURRICANE SHUTTERS THROUGHOUT TO BE READY FOR A STORM IN LESS THAN 20 MINUTES  HOME IS  READY TO MOVE IN. EASY TO SHOW. VACANT
